20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea9aa2d17aa3c7b2b3a038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForsdike%20said%20the%20long%20work%20hours%20under%20China's%20996%20culture%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%3Cp%3EJack%20Forsdike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJack%20Forsdike%20is%20a%20British%20citizen%20who%20worked%20for%20two%20years%20at%20a%20Chinese%20tech%20giant%20in%20Guangzhou.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20experienced%20996%20when%20he%20became%20a%20game%20designer%20in%202024%20and%20soon%20realized%20why%20it's%20dreaded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20BI%20how%20996%20took%20control%20of%20his%20life%20and%20that%20it%20was%20only%20the%20minimum%20of%20the%20expectations%20put%20on%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jack%20Forsdike%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20British%20expat%20from%20Manchester%20who%20worked%20from%202022%20to%202024%20for%20one%20of%20China's%20biggest%20game%20developers.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Forsdike's%20employment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20learned%20I'd%20be%20subject%20to%20China's%20infamous%20996%20hours%2C%20I%20was%20actually%20excited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20I'd%20worked%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%20in%20Guangzhou%20as%20an%20English-Chinese%20interpreter%20at%20a%20local%20tech%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20passion%20was%20in%20game%20design%2C%20so%20it%20was%20my%20dream%20come%20true%20when%20my%20employer%20offered%20me%20a%20development%20role%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuman%20resources%20straight-up%20told%20me%20that%20my%20hours%20would%20increase%20drastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20interpreter%2C%20I'd%20grown%20accustomed%20to%20a%20knock-off-at-seven%20office%20life.%20Developers%20were%20instead%20expected%20to%20work%20from%2010%20a.m.%20to%2010%20p.m.%20every%20day%2C%20six%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wasn't%20what%20our%20contracts%20said%2C%20but%20it%20was%20understood%20as%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20being%20put%20on%20996%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20being%20recognized.%20I%20had%20this%20idea%20that%20those%20work%20hours%20meant%20I%20was%20on%20a%20serious%2C%20valuable%20team%20and%20that%20my%20productivity%20mattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20soon%20realized%20how%20naive%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Forsdike%20eats%20Chinese%20dishes%20and%20poses%20at%20a%20Pokemon%20exhibit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea9a5ad17aa3c7b2b3a015%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForsdike%20studied%20Chinese%20for%20about%20six%20years%20as%20he%20was%20attending%20university%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20Guangzhou%20to%20work.%3Cp%3EJack%20Forsdike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1157209-2581-40f9-b147-ddd9c5a8b089%5C%22%3ELife%20didn't%20exist%20outside%20996%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20996%20life%20didn't%20start%20immediately%3B%20I'd%20just%20gotten%20married%20and%20asked%20my%20manager%20if%20I%20could%20leave%20the%20office%20early%20on%20some%20days%20and%20not%20work%20every%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20agreed.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20could%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20eventually%2C%20the%20work%20began%20piling%20up.%20I'd%20have%20to%20come%20in%20on%20the%20odd%20Saturday%20or%20Sunday.%20On%20some%20days%2C%20I%20started%20leaving%20work%20at%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20months%2C%20my%20996%20schedule%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20I%20spent%20my%20waking%20hours%20either%20leaving%20the%20office%2C%20being%20in%20the%20office%2C%20or%20getting%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20weekends%20wasn't%20going%20to%20get%20me%20a%20pat%20on%20my%20shoulder.%20Even%20on%20Sundays%2C%20I%20found%20out%20it%20was%20normal%20to%20see%20a%20third%20of%20the%20office%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20month%20was%20April%2C%20when%20my%20team%20was%20under%20pressure%20to%20meet%20a%20deadline.%20Western%20game%20developers%20use%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bcrunch%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20grinding%20unpaid%20overtime%20before%20a%20big%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENormal%20996%20already%20felt%20like%20%26quot%3Bcrunch%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20this%20was%20%26quot%3Bcrunch%26quot%3B%20on%20steroids.%20There%20was%20a%20period%20when%20I%20worked%2012-%20to%2014-hour%20shifts%20for%20three%20weeks%20straight%20%E2%80%94%20around%2020%20overtime%20days%20in%20the%20office%20without%20any%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22770%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Forsdike%20looks%20glumly%20into%20the%20camera%20as%20he%20snaps%20a%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea960dcfb7f307e5728ff5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BMy%20face%20shape%20is%20like%20a%20potato%2C%26quot%3B%20Forsdike%20wrote%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20a%20day%20he%20worked%20overtime.%3Cp%3EJack%20Forsdike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20typically%20reach%20the%20office%20just%20before%2010%20a.m.%20for%20breakfast%20%E2%80%94%20where%20all%20meals%20were%20subsidized%20at%20the%20company%20canteen.%20Then%2C%20I'd%20work%20until%2012%3A30%20p.m.%20when%20it%20was%20time%20for%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enjoyed%20the%20privilege%20of%20a%2090-minute%20lunch%20break%2C%20during%20which%20I%20could%20grab%20a%20coffee%20with%20office%20friends%20and%20vent%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20so.%20I%20think%20that%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20survived%20the%20996%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20we'd%20work%20again%20before%20grabbing%20a%20quick%20dinner%2C%20after%20which%20we'd%20plow%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20This%20wasn't%20really%20treated%20like%20overtime%20%E2%80%94%20my%20bosses%20regularly%20scheduled%209%20p.m.%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20get%20home%20after%20midnight%2C%20take%20a%20shower%2C%20and%20head%20straight%20to%20bed.%20Then%20I'd%20get%20up%20and%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20outside%20work%20was%20nonexistent.%20I%20was%20barely%20getting%20any%20face%20time%20with%20my%20wife.%20I'd%20stopped%20playing%20tennis%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20hobbies%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20work%20out.%20Every%20meal%20I%20ate%20was%20in%20the%20office%20canteen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Forsdike%20and%20his%20wife%20pose%20for%20a%20photo%20at%20a%20scenic%20mountain%20spot%20for%20tourists.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea9b30ce3009a0fac71d6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221356%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForsdike%20said%20he%20realized%20he'd%20been%20spending%20almost%20no%20time%20with%20his%20new%20wife%20after%20working%20996.%3Cp%3EJack%20Forsdike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20realize%20that%20my%20health%20took%20a%20hit.%20I%20was%20losing%20muscle%20and%20gaining%20weight.%20It%20was%20becoming%20unsustainable%2C%20but%20I%20just%20prayed%20that%20the%20pressure%20might%20lighten%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219cd3a82-99a5-449d-ad23-63da822b4187%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20going%20to%20be%20my%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20continual%20blow%20was%20that%20we%20never%20saw%20the%20senior%20managers%20who%20made%20the%20decisions%20keeping%20us%20in%20the%20office.%20They'd%20assign%20deadlines%20from%20above%2C%20and%20our%20team%20leaders%20were%20powerless%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20hit%20my%20morale%20was%20the%20understanding%20that%20this%20was%20a%20long-haul%20expectation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlenty%20of%20people%20work%20insane%20hours%20back%20home%20in%20the%20UK.%20Yet%20there's%20typically%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20like%20a%20job%20placement%20or%20a%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20996%2C%20these%20hours%20are%20the%20minimum.%20Everyone%2C%20from%20my%20manager%20to%20my%20colleagues%20to%20my%20friends%20in%20other%20teams%2C%20knows%20this%20work%20life%20is%20never-ending%20and%20demanding%2C%20yet%20they%20all%20seem%20resigned%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20996%20as%20the%20industry%20standard%2C%20my%20colleagues%20were%20afraid%20that%20if%20they%20switched%20companies%2C%20they'd%20end%20up%20in%20a%20tougher%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20got%20a%20break%20in%20May.%20Labor%20Day%20is%20one%20of%20China's%20biggest%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Week%26quot%3B%20holidays%2C%20and%20I'd%20negotiated%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20leave%20as%20a%20condition%20for%20switching%20to%20my%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20returned%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20most%20of%20my%20team%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20had%20been%20laid%20off.%20Our%20project%20was%20essentially%20finished%2C%20but%20the%20company%20decided%20to%20roll%20back%20to%20an%20earlier%20stage%20of%20development%20in%20our%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20disappointed%2C%20mostly%20because%20I'd%20just%20worked%20crazy%20hours%20for%20this%20firm.%20But%20a%20wave%20of%20relief%20swept%20over%20me%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E996%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I'd%20been%20missing%20so%20much%20in%20life%20outside%20work%2C%20and%20getting%20laid%20off%20hit%20the%20reset%20button%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Forsdike%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20in%20front%20of%20an%20ice%20sculpture.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea9985cfb7f307e5729070%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22564%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForsdike%20has%20been%20spending%20time%20off%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20Chinese%2C%20in%20Harbin%2C%20which%20is%20famed%20for%20its%20ice%20sculptures.%3Cp%3EJack%20Forsdike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20managers%20need%20to%20know%20that%20the%20996%20mindset%20is%20just%20outdated.%20It%20doesn't%20make%20your%20teams%20more%20productive%20because%20it%20crushes%20morale%2C%20and%20tired%20teams%20make%20more%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20the%20office%20for%20good%20at%20the%20end%20of%20my%2028-day%20notice%20in%20June%2C%20I've%20been%20spending%20some%20time%20away%20from%20work%20with%20my%20wife%20in%20the%20frosty%20city%20of%20Harbin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dream%20is%20still%20to%20make%20games%20in%20China%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20any%20company%20could%20ever%20entice%20me%20to%20work%20996%20hours%20again.%20There's%20just%20too%20much%20I'd%20lose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-china-games-designer-jack-forsdike-working-hours-culture-office-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728261841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea9aa2d17aa3c7b2b3a038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-china-games-designer-jack-forsdike-working-hours-culture-office-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jack%20Forsdike%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20was%20on%20a%20996%20team%20for%20several%20months%20at%20a%20video%20game%20developer.%20He%20says%20he'll%20never%20go%20back%20to%20that%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-china-games-designer-jack-forsdike-working-hours-culture-office-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Slow'%20win%20over%20Pakista