ealth%20and%20relationships%20for%20multi-generational%20families%20%3Cp%3Eshironosov%2FGetty%2C%20Anna%20Kim%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFamily%20offices%20can%20pay%20six-figure%20salaries%20but%20require%20intense%20dedication.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESelecting%20candidates%20often%20boils%20down%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonality%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECandidates%20should%20master%20more%20skills%20that%20add%20value%20and%20learn%20from%20past%20mistakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20work%20for%20family%20offices%20often%20juggle%20much%20more%20than%20just%20spreadsheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20ultra-wealthy%20people%20set%20up%20dedicated%20offices%2C%20which%20could%20have%20a%20handful%20or%20dozens%20of%20employees%2C%20to%20oversee%20their%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsergey-brin-wealth-management-jeff-bezos-family-offices-women-cios-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20philanthropy%2C%20and%20high-end%20toys%2C%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-yachts-owned-by-tech-billionaires-mark-zuckerberg-jeff-bezos-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20yachts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20office%20might%20look%20after%20one%20person's%20money%20in%20one%20city%20or%20that%20of%20multiple%20generations%20across%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamily%20office%20employees%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20can%20be%20paid%20on%20par%20with%2C%20or%20even%20better%20than%2C%20banking%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-salaries-at-blackstone-apollo-kkr-bain-others%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20private%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20top%20finance%20jobs.%20But%20the%20unique%20nature%20of%20the%20job%20means%20headhunters%20are%20often%20looking%20beyond%20basic%20finance%20skills%20when%20scouting%20candidates%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20Singapore%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20global%20hotspot%20to%20set%20up%20family%20offices%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20business-friendly%20environment%20and%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-attracts-ray-dalio-sergey-brin-family-offices-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapital%20gains%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaires%20like%20Ray%20Dalio%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Bridgewater%20Associates%2C%20and%20Google%20co-founder%20Sergey%20Brin%20have%20established%20family%20offices%20in%20the%20city-state.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freliance-industries-mukesh-ambani-new-family-office-singapore-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMukesh%20Ambani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Asia's%20richest%20man%2C%20also%20expanded%20his%20wealth%20management%20operations%20to%20Singapore%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20three%20recruiters%20for%20family%20offices%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20are%20based%20in%20Singapore%2C%20to%20find%20out%20which%20traits%20give%20a%20candidate%20the%20best%20shot%20of%20landing%20a%20job%20in%20a%20family%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22250f7d12-74d8-46a4-828f-083dfef98f32%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Jack%20of%20all%20trades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20corporate%20jobs'%20clearly-defined%20responsibilities%2C%20family%20office%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20even%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20juggle%20a%20lot%2C%20said%20Paul%20Westall%2C%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecofounder%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAgreus%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%20might%20not%20fit%20nicely%20into%20a%20family%20office%20because%2C%20at%20Goldman%2C%20they%20might%20have%2010%20analysts%20and%20two%20assistants%2C%20while%20in%20a%20family%20office%2C%20they%20do%20all%20the%20analysis%20and%20book%20their%20flights%2C%26q