ideas%20and%20came%20up%20with%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20noticing%20how%20temperatures%20in%20my%20hometown%2C%20Bengaluru%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20risen%20drastically%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Even%20the%20monsoon%20months%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20pleasant%2C%20started%20feeling%20like%20summer%20because%20of%20all%20the%20urban%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worried%20me%20that%20there%20weren't%20any%20major%20government%20or%20private%20initiatives%20looking%20to%20improve%20things%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20tech%20giants%20I%20worked%20at%20were%20looking%20at%20climate%20solutions%20indirectly.%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20an%20e-commerce%20platform%20that%20aims%20to%20improve%20urban%20greenery.%20It%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20combine%20two%20things%20I%20love%2C%20technology%20and%20gardening%2C%20which%20was%20always%20my%20escape%20when%20things%20got%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20launched%20my%20startup%20in%20January%20and%20have%20been%20working%20on%20scaling%20it%20up%20since.%20I%20have%20also%20built%20a%20mentorship%20and%20job%20readiness%20platform%20to%20help%20those%20looking%20for%20career%20guidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20my%20ventures%20are%20bootstrapped%20and%20I%20only%20plan%20to%20bring%20on%20any%20partners%20if%20they%20are%20a%20strategic%20fit.%20I%20don't%20want%20the%20pressure%20of%20an%20investor%20pushing%20me%20to%20make%20decisions%20that%20only%20have%20a%20financial%20benefit%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20lose%20sight%20of%20my%20original%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270f8cf9f-715a-43fd-b16e-96db0ba61193%5C%22%3EBureaucracy%20and%20big%20commutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20being%20back%20home%2C%20but%20there%20are%20challenges.%20India%20is%20still%20not%20among%20the%20highest-ranked%20countries%20for%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%2C%20and%20I%20have%20faced%20bureaucracy%20when%20setting%20up%20my%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20to%20make%20sacrifices%20as%20a%20family%20too.%20My%20wife%20is%20still%20working%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company%20and%20spends%20much%20more%20time%20commuting%20than%20she%20did%20back%20in%20the%20US.%20I%20have%20two%20daughters%2C%20and%20inequality%20in%20Indian%20workplaces%20and%20concerns%20for%20their%20safety%20also%20weigh%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20different%20joy%20in%20building%20solutions%20for%20India%20and%20the%20problems%20that%20I%20grew%20up%20around%2C%20like%20improving%20local%20greenery%20and%20better%20access%20to%20mentorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20advantage%20is%20that%20the%20Indian%20market%20is%20chaotic.%20Even%20long-established%20players%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20figure%20it%20out%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20new%20entrants.%20The%20market%20size%20has%20also%20been%20encouraging.%20One%20of%20our%20first%20orders%20came%20from%20the%20opposite%20end%20of%20the%20country%2C%20which%20was%20surprising%20because%20we%20had%20not%20even%20begun%20marketing%20or%20search%20engine%20optimization%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20importantly%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20found%20what%20was%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20heard%20my%20parents%20talking%20about%20their%20regrets%20and%20things%20they%20wanted%20to%20do.%20I%20didn't%20want%20any%20regrets%20when%20telling%20my%20kids%20about%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20myself%3A%20I'll%20explore%20my%20own%20venture%20for%20five%20to%2010%20years%20and%20go%20back%20to%20a%20corporate%20job%20if%20things%20don't%20work%20out.%20I'll%20have%20a%20bigger%20experience%20and%20a%20better%20story%20to%20tell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDid%20you%20leave%20Big%20Tech%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20field%3F%20Please%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%3A%20shubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3