%20get%20off%20the%20bike%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20eyewitness%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20medical%20officer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOnly%20after%20the%20postmortem%20examination%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20cause%20of%20death%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20are%20being%20raised%20over%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20aggressively%20pushing%20this%20event%20to%20set%20a%20Limca%20Book%20of%20World%20Record%20by%20aiming%20to%20mobilise%2015%20lakh%20spectators%20--%20much%20beyond%20manageable%20--%20and%20the%20Chennai%20City%20Police's%20poor%20crowd%20and%20traffic%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20had%20been%20going%20smoothly%20ahead%20of%20the%20event%2C%20with%20largescale%20traffic%20diversion%20and%20parking%20regulations.%20But%20closer%20to%20the%20air%20show%20--%20scheduled%20at%2011%20am%20--%20the%20crowd%20got%20so%20large%20that%20the%20elevated%20MRTS%20railway%20stations%20along%20the%20Marina%20Beach%20road%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20sea%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaos%20broke%20out%20after%20the%20event%20when%20the%20entire%20crowd%20started%20to%20disperse.%20Every%20inch%20of%20the%20space%20on%20the%20Beach%20road%20appeared%20occupied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20adequate%20arrangement%20for%20drinking%20water%20in%20the%20spectators'%20area.%20With%20temperature%20soaring%20and%20no%20public%20transport%2C%20hundreds%20had%20to%20walk%20three%20to%20four%20kilometres%20on%20the%20jam-packed%20roads%20to%20get%20any%20public%20conveyance%20or%20pick%20up%20their%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20-%20children%20among%20them%20--%20just%20sat%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20tired%20and%20dehydrated.%20Many%20were%20seen%20attending%20to%20fainted%20or%20weary%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20effective%20police%20regulation%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20vehicles%20and%20two%20wheelers%20haphazardly%20entered%20both%20ways%20and%20remained%20stuck%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20on%20most%20roads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20police%20personnel%20were%20busy%20returning%20on%20their%20two%20wheelers%2C%20turning%20into%20mute%20spectators.%20They%20%C2%A0neither%20regulated%20the%20situation%20nor%20intervened%20to%20help%20stranded%20%C2%A0ambulances%20until%20there%20was%20public%20uproar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20drinking%20water%20stations%20along%20the%20roads.%20Most%20eateries%20on%20these%20stretches%20were%20shut%20and%20shops%20that%20were%20open%20ran%20out%20of%20water%20and%20soft%20drinks%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mother%20who%20had%20brought%20her%20%C2%A0two%20children%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20us.%20No%20proper%20arrangements%20at%20all%20either%20at%20the%20venue%20or%20on%20the%20roads%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chennai%20police%20had%20deployed%206%2C500%20police%20personnel%20and%201%2C500%20home%20guards%20for%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20--%20which%20has%20a%20culture%20of%20objecting%20to%20mass%20gatherings%20citing%20security%20concerns%20--%20had%20expressed%20its%20concern%20to%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20advised%20against%20hyping%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Ma%20Subramanian%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20the%20state%20Chief%20Secretary%20had%20presided%20over%20a%20coordination%20meeting%20with%20IAF%20and%20other%20officials%20had%20held%20several%20meetings.%20%26quot%3BArrangements%20were%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20IAF's%20demands.%20The%20Chennai%20Corporation%20and%20Metro%20Water%20too%20had%20made%20adequate%20temporary%20toilets%20and%20drinking%20water%20arrangements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20note%20with%20no%20attribution%20claimed%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20dead%20in%20the%20crowd.%20No%20death%20is%20related%20to%20crowd%20or%20mismanagement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20show%20had%20included%20a%20show%20by%20the%20Special%20Garud%20Force%20commandos%20in%20a%20simulated%20rescue%20operation%20and%20in%20freeing%20the%20hostage.%20It%20also%20showcased%2072%20aircraft%2C%20including%20Rafale%2C%20indigenously%20manufactured%20state-of-the-art%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20Tejas%2C%20Light%20Combat%20helicopter%20Prachand%2C%20and%20Heritage%20aircraft%20Dakota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728237420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fl02uuhj8_marina-air-show-ani_625x300_06_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-spectators-dead-at-indian-air-forces-airshow-conducted-at-chennais-marina-beach-6730230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20persons%20who%20went%20to%20watch%20the%20air%20show%20at%20Chennai's%20Marina%20Beach%20have%20died.%20Doctors%20said%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%20had%20heat%20stroke.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bowen%3A%20Year%20of%20killing%20and%20broken%20assumptions%20has%20taken%20Middle%20East%20to%20edge%20of%20deeper%2C%20wider%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728236817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F991f%2Flive%2F891b49d0-8403-11ef-822c-a50726bfda2e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc781vgy3918o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twelve%20months%20on%20from%20the%207%20October%20attacks%20which%20led%20to%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20our%20international%20editor%20says%20the%20region%20is%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20something%20even%20worse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A238%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc781vgy3918o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampprojec