gers%20at%20Toadstool%20Caf%C3%A9.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20main%20purpose%20of%20our%20visit%20was%20to%20experience%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20to%20secure%20a%20spot%20at%20the%20land's%20restaurant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-toadstool-cafe-super-nintendo-world-mario-luigi-burger-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToadstool%20Caf%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20we%20spent%20%2471.40%20on%20unique%20food%20items%20like%20Mario-%20and%20Luigi-inspired%20burgers%20and%20themed%20spaghetti%2C%20plus%20cute%20appetizers%20and%20drinks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20featured%20immersive%20d%C3%A9cor%2C%20and%20the%20food%20was%20very%20Instagram-worthy.%20Given%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20meal%2C%20the%20pricing%20felt%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20snacked%20on%20oversized%20pretzels%2C%20Butterbeers%20(and%20regular%20beers)%20in%20the%20park's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-wizarding-world-harry-potter-universal-what-to-skip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWizarding%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plus%20other%20treats%20that%20left%20us%20full%20and%20our%20wallets%20only%20a%20little%20lighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPower-Up%20Bands%20were%20essential%20to%20our%20visit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20wrists%20putting%20their%20red%2C%20white%2C%20and%20blue%20Power-Up%20wristbands%20together%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f55739de59ade1a3b4b80e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPower-Up%20Bands%20enhanced%20our%20visit%20to%20Super%20Nintendo%20World.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20family%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20souvenirs.%20We%20bought%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-nintendo-world-park-is-beautiful-but-experience-was-confusing-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPower-Up%20Bands%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2442%20each%20%E2%80%94%20they%20connect%20to%20themed%20games%20throughout%20Super%20Nintendo%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20pricey%2C%20these%20bands%20were%20necessary%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20fully%20enjoy%20this%20land's%20interactive%20features%20and%20engage%20in%20friendly%20competition%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20I%20wish%20we%20skipped%20the%20wand%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B-themed%20land.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wand%20on%20top%20of%20a%20map%20from%20Olivander's%20in%20Harry%20Potter%20Wizarding%20World%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f55739de59ade1a3b4b810%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20son%20isn't%20a%20huge%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20fan%20so%20he%20forgot%20about%20this%20wand%20pretty%20quickly.%20%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20souvenirs%2C%20I%20wish%20we%20hadn't%20bought%20the%20interactive%20wand%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B-themed%20Wizarding%20World%2C%20which%20cost%20almost%20%2465.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20was%20selected%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20ceremony%20at%20the%20park's%20wand%20shop%2C%20Ollivanders%2C%20and%20although%20the%20show%20was%20cute%2C%20we%20felt%20compelled%20to%20buy%20the%20wand%20that%20%26quot%3Bchose%20him.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he's%20not%20really%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-ending-of-harry-potter-series-was-bad-opinion-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20souvenir%20was%20quickly%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20other%20souvenirs%20served%20a%20more%20practical%20purpose%20and%20hold%20a%20special%20place%20in%20our%20hearts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pihranna%20plant%20figurine%20in%20front%20of%20Nintendo%20World%20poster%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f55739de59ade1a3b4b80f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20son%20chose%20posters%20and%20a%20Piranha%20Plant%20lamp%20for%20his%20new%20bedroom.%20%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Adler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20magic%20wands%20and%20interactive%20bracelets%2C%20we%20spent%20an%20additional%20%24110.28%20on%20souvenirs.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20these%20served%20a%20more%20practical%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20traveled%20to%20California%2C%20we%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20selling%20our%20home.%20With%20numerous%20showings%20and%20open%20houses%20scheduled%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20out%20of%20our%20home%20for%20several%20days.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20staying%20in%20a%20hotel%20close%20to%20home%2C%20one%20reason%20we%20chose%20to%20visit%20Hollywood%20was%20because%20my%20son%20was%20nervous%20about%20moving.%20I%20felt%20that%20taking%20him%20to%20this%20%26quot%3Bdream%26quot%3B%20locale%20would%20be%20a%20welcome%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20leaving%20Universal%20Hollywood%2C%20we%20allowed%20him%20to%20pick%20out%20several%20souvenirs%20that%20he%20could%20use%20to%20decorate%20his%20room%20at%20our%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Piranha%20Plant%20lamp%20and%20posters%20he%20selected%20helped%20him%20to%20personalize%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20embrace%20his%20new%20space%2C%20making%20these%20items%20an%20enduring%20and%20worthwhile%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fu