%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20Nations%20is%20like%20an%20old%20company%2C%20not%20entirely%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20market%2C%20but%20occupying%20the%20space...What%20you%20have%20today%20is%2C%20yes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20UN.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20however%20suboptimal%20it%20is%20in%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAFFTf9ScHo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAFFTf9ScHo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1842852176911372755%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20took%20part%20in%20the%20interactive%20session%20on%20'India%20and%20the%20Globe'%20and%20spoke%20of%20India's%20role%20and%20challenges%20amid%20changing%20global%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20are%20both%20a%20lifting%20tide%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20paradoxical%20one%2C%20a%20ballast%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20as%20he%20enumerated%20some%20of%20the%20steps%20India%20has%20taken%20to%20help%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20its%20neighbours%20such%20as%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20a%20summit%20of%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%2C%20he%20again%20sought%20to%20rule%20out%20any%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20his%20Pakistani%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20there%20for%20a%20certain%20job%2C%20a%20certain%20responsibility.%20And%2C%20I%20take%20my%20responsibilities%20seriously.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20going%20there%20to%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20SCO%20meeting%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20I%20am%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20Islamabad%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmultilateral%20event%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20to%20discuss%20India-Pakistan%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%20to%20a%20query%20on%20the%20United%20Nations'%20role%20amid%20the%20changing%20global%20scenario%2C%20he%20took%20a%20rather%20critical%20view%20of%20the%20world%20body%20that%20was%20born%20in%201945%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20Initially%2C%20it%20had%2050%20countries%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20over%20these%20years%20to%20nearly%20four%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UN%20is%20in%20a%20way%20like%20an%20old%20company%2C%20not%20entirely%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20market%2C%20but%20occupying%20the%20space.%20And%2C%20when%20it's%20behind%20times%2C%20in%20this%20world%20you%20have%20start-ups%20and%20innovations%2C%20so%20different%20people%20start%20doing%20their%20own%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20what%20you%20have%20today%20is%20that%20yes%20you%20have%20a%20UN%20at%20the%20end%2C%20however%20suboptimal%20in%20functioning%2C%20it%20is%20still%20the%20only%20multilateral%20game%20in%20town%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20when%20it%20doesn't%20step%20up%20on%20key%20issues%2C%20countries%20figure%20out%20their%20own%20ways%20of%20doing%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20let's%20take%20the%20last%20five-10%20years%2C%20probably%20the%20biggest%20thing%20that%20happened%20in%20our%20life%20was%20Covid.%20Now%2C%20what%20did%20the%20UN%20do%20on%20Covid%3F%20I%20think%20the%20answer%20is%20--%20not%20very%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20you%20have%20two%20conflicts%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%20two%20very%20serious%20conflicts%2C%20where%20is%20the%20UN%20on%20them%2C%20essentially%20a%20bystander%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20as%20it%20did%20during%20Covid%20also%2C%20countries%20did%20their%20own%20thing%20such%20as%20the%20initiative%20like%20Covax%20that%20was%20done%20by%20a%20group%20of%20countries%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20big%20issues%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you%20have%20an%20increasing%20combination%20of%20countries%20coming%20together%20to%20agree%20to%20do%20something.%26quot%3B%20He%20cited%20the%20examples%20of%20connectivity%20initiatives%20like%20the%20India-MiddleEast-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%2C%20QUAD%20in%20Indo-Pacific%20to%20look%20after%20the%20global%20commons%2C%20the%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%20(ISA)%20and%20the%20Coalition%20for%20Disaster%20Resilient%20Infrastructure%20(CDRI)%2C%20saying%20all%20these%20bodies%20came%20outside%20the%20UN%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20UN%20will%20continue%2C%20but%20increasingly%20there%20is%20a%20non-UN%20space%20which%20is%20the%20active%20space%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20telling%20on%20the%20UN%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2075%20years%20after%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20still%20working%20to%20maintain%20international%20peace%20and%20security%2C%20give%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%20protect%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20uphold%20international%20law%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20demanding%20reforms%20in%20the%20world%20body%20and%20its%20UN%20Security%20Council%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20changed%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20suggested%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bshort-sighted%26quot%3B%20approach%20of%20the%20five%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UNSC%20is%20holding%20back%20forward%20movement%20in%20the%20long-pending%20reform%20of%20the%20global%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20permanent%20members%20are%20Russia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20China%2C%20France%20and%20the%20US%20and%20these%20countries%20can%20veto%20any%20substantive%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20was%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20outcome%20of%20the%20US%20elections%20and%20how%20will%20India%20engage%20with%20the%20new%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20spoke%20of%20one%20possibility%20of%20the%20two%20in%20the%20American%20elections.%20I%20stress%20to%20you%2C%20look%20back%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20how%20many%20of%20the%20policies%20which%20in%202020%20people%20thought%20were%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20policies%20actually%20not%20just%20carried%20over%20by%20Biden%20but%20they%20doubled%20down%20on%20those%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20this%20is%20not%20just%20a%20politician%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20fashion%2C%20just%20one%20administration.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20very%20deep%20shifts%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is...%20America%20which%20actually%20has%20made%20a%20shift%2C%20geopolitically%20and%20in%20its%20economic%20outlook%20and%20has%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20order%20which%20itself%20devised%20many%20years%20ago%20no%20longer%20works%20to%20its%20benefit%20to%20that%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20would%20argue%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20outcomes%20in%20November%2C%20many%20of%20these%20trends%20will%20intensify%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20And%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20get%2C%20I%20would%20call%20it%20a%20more%20fractured%20world%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20reliability%20and%20transparency%20are%20going%20to%20be%20two%20very%20key%20factors%20which%20will%20become%20a%20metric%20for%20countries%20to%20have%20enterprises%20and%20domains%20to%20have%20dealings%20with%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20it%20itself%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20value%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%