quot%3Bvery%20casual%20girly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20my%20career%20started%20to%20evolve%2C%20jewelry%20was%20a%20symbol%20of%20showing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20my%20armor%20in%20a%20way.%20I'm%20braving%20myself%20for%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Rae%20continued.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20I%20don't%20feel%20luxurious%2C%20even%20though%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I'm%20worthy%20to%20show%20up%20here%2C%20what%20I'm%20wearing%20makes%20it%20seem%20like%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERae%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcastjewelry.com%2Fcollections%2Fbraeve%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Braeve%20Collection%2C%20her%20collaboration%20with%20Cast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco-based%20jewelry%20company%2C%20had%20to%20be%20approachable%20for%20it%20to%20make%20sense.%20The%2022-piece%20collection%2C%20ranging%20in%20price%20from%20%24250%20to%20%245%2C900%2C%20features%20a%20variety%20of%20geometric%20hoops%2C%20cuffs%2C%20rings%2C%20necklaces%2C%20and%20pendants%20in%20finishes%20ranging%20from%20sterling%20silver%20to%2014K%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20she%20hoped%20the%20price%20range%20%26quot%3Bwas%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20for%20the%20girl%20who's%20just%20like%2C%20'I%20deserve.%20I%20wanna%20treat%20myself.%20I'm%20ready%20to%20level%20up%2C'%20and%20that's%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20board%20%E2%80%94%20the%20girl%20I%20want%20to%20approach%2C%20the%20girl%20that%20I'm%20talking%20to%20in%20my%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20entrepreneur%20with%20her%20hand%20in%20many%20pots%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%20the%20mindset%20that%20propels%20Rae%20in%20business%20%E2%80%94%20to%20what%20she%20credits%20her%20success%2C%20the%20red%20flags%20she%20looks%20out%20for%20in%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20how%20she%20can%20create%20so%20effectively.%20Here's%20what%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb154b90-d1e9-41ba-a912-9fc99fdf3cad%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERae%20credits%20this%20one%20skill%20to%20her%20success%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20writer%20said%20waking%20up%20at%204%20a.m.%20is%20her%20cheat%20code.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20by%20saying%20I'm%20gonna%20get%20up%20at%207%20today%3B%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20up%20at%206%2C%20and%20then%20it%20became%204%20%E2%80%94%20and%204%20has%20been%20a%20game%20changer%2C%20honestly.%20Nobody%20else%20is%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%20much%20of%20the%20pressure%20is%20I'm%20always%20behind%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20felt%20like%20I'm%20not%20behind%20anymore%2C%20and%20I%20get%20my%20own%20self-care%20time%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERae%20also%20noted%20that%20she%20didn't%20have%20any%20other%20time%20that%20was%20her%20own%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20now%20it's%20become%20the%20only%20part%20of%20my%20day%20that%20I%20could%20fully%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20it%20to%20work%20out%2C%20which%20she%20considers%20her%20own%20form%20of%20active%20meditation%2C%20in%20her%20garage%20gym.%20She%20then%20journals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20waking%20up%20for%20me%20and%20not%20for%20other%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483591e5-5422-48ca-ad70-ab6807366633%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20actor%20says%20a%20creative's%20first%20hire%20should%20be%20a%20TV%20producer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20look%20at%20a%20successful%20actor%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20standing%20behind%2C%20beside%2C%20and%20in%20front%20of%20them%20who%20make%20their%20achievements%20possible.%20Rae%20said%20when%20building%20her%20team%2C%20her%20first%20hire%20was%20her%20most%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20met%20Deniese%2C%20that's%20all%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20produce.%20That%20changed%20the%20game%20for%20me%20because%20that's%20a%20person%20who's%20just%20interested%20in%20executing%20and%20making%20things%20happen%2C%20pulling%20the%20people%20together%20to%20make%20your%20ideas%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained%2C%20referring%20to%20producer%20Deniese%20Davis.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20produced%20Rae's%20hit%20shows%2C%20%26quot%3BAwkward%20Black%20Girl%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BInsecure.%26quot%3B%20She's%20also%20the%20cofounder%20of%20the%20management%20company%20ColorCreative%2C%20which%20she%20created%20with%20Rae%20and%20producer%20Talitha%20Watkins%20in%202014%20to%20support%20women%20and%20minority%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Issa%20Rae%20wearing%20yellow%20while%20holding%20her%20hand%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f9a8ce75c877a99b619506%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECast%20Jewelry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%2C%20'I%20wanna%20do%20this%20project%2C%20and%20she's%20like%2C%20'Cool.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20make%20this%20happen'%20because%20I%20can't%20do%20it%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20the%20'how'%20person%2C%20the%20'these-are-the-steps'%20person.%20To%20someone%20else%20outside%20the%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20maybe%20that's%20a%20project%20manager.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22357b153d-96bd-4e91-a24f-e5ce9f357324%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERae's%20biggest%20red%20flag%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20participating%20in%20collaborations%20is%20based%20on%20honesty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Rae%20has%20signed%20onto%20many%20collaborations%20and%20partnerships%2C%20she's%20also%20learned%20when%20to%20say%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they're%20just%20solely%20driven%20by%20money%2C%20and%20if%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20can't%20be%20fully%20honest%20in%20the%20criticism%20aspect%2C%20and%20they%20can't%20be%20honest%20with%20me%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20this%20won't%20work%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20d