D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-energy-electricity-data-centers-fossil-fuels-tech-revolution-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20execs%20to%20turn%20to%20fossil%20fuels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20threaten%20those%20net-zero%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt's%20comments%20came%20at%20an%20AI%20summit%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20where%20he%20addressed%20the%20crowd%20and%20gave%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20future%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Schmidt%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20CEO%20from%202001%20to%202011%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20also%20previously%20chaired%20the%20National%20Security%20Commission%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20at%20the%20event%20that%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20curb%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-generative-ai-environment-climate-change-global-emissions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enegative%20effects%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20have%20on%20the%20environment%2C%20like%20using%20better%20batteries%20and%20power%20lines%20to%20build%20data%20centers%2C%20but%20he%20thinks%20AI%20growth%20will%20eventually%20outpace%20these%20preventive%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20that%20will%20be%20swamped%20by%20the%20enormous%20needs%20of%20this%20new%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20told%20the%20crowd.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20a%20universal%20technology%2C%20and%20because%20it's%20the%20arrival%20of%20an%20alien%20intelligence%E2%80%A6%20we%20may%20make%20mistakes%20with%20respect%20to%20how%20it's%20used%2C%20but%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20there%20through%20conservation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresenters%20pressed%20Schmidt%20on%20whether%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20meet%20AI%20energy%20needs%20without%20disregarding%20conservation%20goals.%2