ince%20the%20wedge%20driven%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20last%20year%20over%20President%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20One%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20terrorists%2C%20Nijjar%20was%20also%20a%20Canadian%20citizen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20before%20the%20foreign%20interference%20commission%20in%20Ottawa%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20Canada's%20Deputy%20Minister%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%20David%20Morrison%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BCanada's%20policy%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20India's%20territorial%20integrity%20must%20be%20respected.%20There's%20one%20India%2C%20and%20that's%20been%20made%20very%20clear%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%20living%20in%20Canada%2C%20he%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bawful%20but%20lawful%26quot%3B.%20There%20are%20things%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20us%20want%20not%20to%20see%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20are%20protected%20under%20Freedom%20of%20Speech%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20about%20One%20India%2C%20however%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20clarify%20Ottawa's%20position%20on%20the%20stance%20of%20Khalistanis%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20Canadian%20citizens.%20The%20comment%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20signal%20to%20put%20India-Canada%20relations%20--%20which%20have%20been%20on%20a%20free%20fall%20--%20on%20an%20even%20keel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20been%20sending%20feelers%20to%20India%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20got%20elected%20for%20a%20historic%20third%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20that%20talks%20with%20India%20can%20now%20resume%20on%20%26quot%3Bsome%20very%20serious%20issues%20around%20national%20security%20and%20keeping%20Canadians%20safe%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20India%20had%20rejected%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20concern%20about%20Canada%20becoming%20a%20hub%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20Sikhs.%20Canada%20had%20not%20acknowledged%20it.%20Instead%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20Canada%20will%20always%20%26quot%3Bdefend%20freedom%20of%20expression...%20conscience%20and%20peaceful%20protest%26quot%3B.%20It%20will%20also%20prevent%20violence%20and%20push%20back%20against%20hatred%2C%20he%20had%20amended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilateral%20relations%2C%20subsequently%2C%20had%20plummeted%2C%20and%20trade%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20had%20got%20derailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20had%20observed%20a%20moment%20of%20silence%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20Nijjar.%20India%20had%20responded%20with%20a%20memorial%20service%20in%20Vancouver%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20the%20329%20victims%20of%20the%20Air%20India%20flight%20bombed%20by%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20in%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%2045%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20unidentified%20gunmen%20on%20June%2018%20last%20year%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20arrested%20four%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20course%20of%20their%20investigations.%20India%20had%20said%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20interests%20at%20work%26quot%3B%20and%20reiterated%20that%20separatists%20have%20been%20given%20political%20space%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728218700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fs03v9e98_modi-trudeau_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftheres-one-india-canada-reaffirms-support-for-territorial-integrity-6729296%22%2C%2