f%20possibilities%20in%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20assembly%20elections.%20While%20exit%20polls%20for%20Haryana%20indicate%20a%20common%20direction%2C%20with%20some%20variation%20in%20numbers%2C%20the%20projections%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20lend%20themselves%20to%20multiple%20interpretations.%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20projected%20numbers%20in%20both%20cases%20helps%20identify%20the%20key%20factors%20shaping%20the%20electoral%20politics%20in%20these%20two%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Clear%20Majority%20For%20Congress%20In%20Haryana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20projected%20to%20secure%20a%20clear%20majority.%20While%20the%20margin%20of%20that%20majority%20differs%20from%20poll%20to%20poll%2C%20the%20general%20direction%20of%20the%20results%20appears%20consistent.%20Five%20factors%20are%20worth%20considering%20when%20analysing%20these%20trends.%20First%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20completing%20two%20terms%20in%20office%20and%20is%20seeking%20a%20third.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20came%20to%20power%20through%20an%20alliance%20with%20a%20regional%20party%2C%20an%20alliance%20that%20fell%20apart%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20five-year%20term.%20Indications%20suggest%20that%20Haryana%20witnessed%20a%20direct%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20with%20state-based%20players%20largely%20marginalised%2C%20except%20in%20a%20few%20minor%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20have%20been%20discussed.%20However%2C%20anti-incumbency%20alone%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20unseat%20a%20government.%20A%20strong%2C%20visible%2C%20viable%2C%20and%20aggressive%20challenger%20is%20needed%20to%20capitalize%20on%20that%20sentiment%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20have%20played%20that%20role%20effectively%20during%20the%20campaign.%20Third%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20faced%20internal%20conflicts%20over%20seat%20distribution%2C%20shifting%20political%20loyalties%2C%20leadership%20competition%2C%20and%20open%20expressions%20of%20dissent.%20The%20results%20will%20reflect%20which%20party%20managed%20these%20challenges%20more%20effectively.%20Additionally%2C%20both%20the%20BJP's%20and%20Congress's%20vote%20shares%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20compared%20to%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls%2C%20given%20the%20near%20two-way%20contest%20in%20the%20state%2C%20though%20this%20increase%20may%20not%20be%20fully%20reflected%20in%20seat%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Jat-vs-Non-Jat%20Competition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20the%20state's%20caste%20dynamics%20may%20be%20undergoing%20a%20shift.%20Traditionally%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20Jat%20vs.%20non-Jat%20competition.%20Since%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20performed%20well%20among%20non-Jat%20segments%2C%20while%20the%20Jat%20vote%20has%20often%20been%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20state%20players.%20If%20the%20exit%20poll%20trends%20hold%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20consolidated%20the%20Jat%20vote%20and%20made%20inroads%20among%20non-Jat%20segments%20as%20well.%20The%20%26quot%3BJAPKI%26quot%3B%20factor-Jawan%20(soldier)%2C%20Pehalwan%20(wrestler)%2C%20and%20Kisan%20(farmer)-would%20likely%20have%20worked%20in%20Congress's%20favour%20if%20these%20trends%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20the%20youth%20vote%20will%20be%20critical%20in%20Haryana.%20Voters%20under%2030%20have%20participated%20in%20elections%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20their%20aspirations%20and%20vision%20could%20play%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%20Key%20Factors%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20issues%20are%20markedly%20different.%20Exit%20polls%20suggest%20that%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)-Congress%20alliance%20is%20ahead%2C%20though%20many%20do%20not%20predict%20a%20clear%20majority%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20four%20factors%20are%20at%20play.%20First%2C%20there%20is%20a%20notable%20divergence%20in%20trends%20between%20the%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20The%20BJP%20is%20strong%20in%20Jammu%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20establish%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20Valley.%20Within%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%2C%20the%20NC%20dominates%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20focuses%20more%20on%20Jammu.%20The%20PDP%2C%20smaller%20state%20parties%2C%20and%20independents%20also%20have%20a%20presence%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20key%20focus%20on%20October%208%20will%20be%20which%20party%20emerges%20as%20the%20single%20largest.%20Though%20the%20NC%20and%20Congress%20have%20an%20alliance%2C%20they%20contested%20some%20seats%20against%20each%20other%2C%20weakening%20their%20claim%20as%20a%20pre-poll%20alliance.%20If%20they%20collectively%20secure%20a%20majority%2C%20their%20position%20will%20be%20strengthened.%20However%2C%20if%20no%20party%20crosses%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20could%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20decision.%20Additionally%2C%20if%20neither%20the%20BJP%20nor%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%20wins%20a%20majority%2C%20the%20smaller%20state-based%20parties%20and%20independents%20will%20become%20pivotal.%20How%20far%20the%20largest%20party%20or%20alliance%20falls%20from%20the%20majority%20will%20also%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20if%20no%20party%20or%20alliance%20reaches%20the%20halfway%20mark%2C%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20PDP%2C%20other%20state-level%20players%2C%20and%20independents%20will%20be%20critical.%20Given%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20likely%20win%20most%20of%20its%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20while%20these%20other%20groups%20would%20dominate%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%20the%20political%20dynamics%20of%20post-election%20support%20will%20hinge%20on%20the%20distinct%20politics%20of%20the%20two%20regions.%20During%20the%20campaign%2C%20these%20smaller%20players%20raised%20various%20issues.%20The%20question%20will%20be%20whether%20their%20issues%20align%20more%20with%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%2C%20or%20if%20post-election%20politics%20will%20follow%20different%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20assembly%20election%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20the%20region%20has%20seen%20significant%20changes%20during%20that%20time.%20The%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20division%20of%20the%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20have%20had%20far-reaching%20implications.%20The%20election%20results%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20response%20to%20these%20changes.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20nominate%20five%20members%20to%20the%20assembly%2C%20with%20nominated%20members%20having%20the%20same%20status%20as%20elected%20ones.%20This%20could%20potentially%20alter%20the%20balance%20in%20terms%20of%20securing%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20elections%20have%20significant%20long-term%20implications.%20As%20the%20first%20polls%20following%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20their%20outcomes%20could%20influence%20the%20political%20landscape%20not%20only%20in%20the%20regions%20where%20the%20elections%20were%20held%20but%20across%20the%20country.%20Two%20more%20major%20state%20elections%20are%20set%20to%20follow%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20making%20the%20October%208%20results%20the%20first%20in%20a%20series%20of%20important%20contests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20is%20the%20National%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Lokniti%20Network)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728218160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2