%20be%20held%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20Two%20cities%20Riyadh%20and%20Jeddah%20have%20been%20chosen%20as%20the%20probable%20venues%20for%20two-day%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenowned%20Portugal%20football%20star%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo%20also%20plays%20in%20the%20Saudi%20Arabian%20club%2C%20Al-Nassr.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20stated%20that%20London%20was%20also%20being%20considered%20as%20a%20probable%20venue%20but%20the%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20city%20forced%20to%20BCCI%20to%20drop%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20retention%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aakash%20Chopra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F597-aakash-chopra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAakash%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20bag%20a%20mega%20deal%20if%20he%20is%20to%20enter%20the%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20is%20KL%20Rahul.%20He%20is%20the%20face%20of%20the%20franchise%20and%20you%20would%20want%20to%20make%20him%20the%20captain.%20You%20are%20not%20going%20to%20get%20him%20for%20RS%2018%20crore.%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%20if%20he%20goes%20to%20the%20auction%2C%20he%20will%20get%20Rs%2018%20crore.%20Anyways%20you%20never%20leave%20the%20captain.%20For%20continuity%20that%20is%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Aakash%20Chopra%20said%20in%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20LSG's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115355-mayank-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMayank%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20been%20selected%20in%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20T20Is%2C%20Chopra%20had%20an%20interesting%20take.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20have%20definitely