er%20and%20daughter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20wedding%2C%20Mukta%20chose%20to%20complement%20her%20look%20with%20a%20metallic%20grey%20saree%20instead%20of%20the%20customary%20bright-coloured%20clothing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20compliments%20and%20attention.%20The%20photographs%20came%20out%20beautifully%2C%20and%20I%20posted%20them%20on%20Instagram%2C%20tagging%20the%20designer.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20designer%20reached%20out%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20photograph%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20modelling%20for%20the%20designer%2C%20Mukta%20started%20receiving%20numerous%20opportunities%20from%20popular%20designers%20who%20were%20eager%20to%20promote%20inclusivity%20and%20drive%20change.%20Through%20these%20unexpected%20opportunities%20in%20the%20modelling%20world%2C%20she%20found%20a%20platform%20to%20celebrate%20her%20unique%20style%20and%20individuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20finally%20time%20for%20me%20to%20celebrate%20my%20life%20and%20the%20desires%20I%20had%20kept%20hidden%20%E2%80%94%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333328%2Fujjain-beautician-monisha-chhabra-broke-makeup-taboos-empowered-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20cosmetics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20clothes%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20pull%20off.%20I%20no%20longer%20deprive%20myself%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20I%20am%20fulfilling%20my%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukta%20strongly%20believes%20in%20the%20power%20of%20self-respect%20and%20self-worth%2C%20transcending%20age%20barriers%20while%20embracing%20every%20stage%20of%20life%20with%20joy%20and%20confidence.%20Speaking%20about%20societal%20expectations%20for%20women%20her%20age%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20woman%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20family%2C%20but%20that%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20at%2