rience.%20Recently%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20post%20of%20a%20company%20hiring%20project%20engineers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20.NET%20developers%20with%20experience%20of%20six%20to%20eight%20years.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20they%20mentioned%20a%20willingness%20to%20accept%20job%20applications%20of%20persons%20with%20a%20gap%20of%20up%20to%20four%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20feedback%20we%20got%20from%20those%20applying%20was%20that%20they%20were%20offered%20a%20salary%20of%20just%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20When%20asked%20why%20the%20applicants%20were%20offered%20such%20a%20low%20salary%2C%20the%20companies%20said%20that%20they%20will%20help%20applicants%20undergo%20training%20for%20three%20months.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20at%20the%20company%2C%20these%20applicants%20will%20qualify%20for%20appraisals.%20Given%20the%20paucity%20of%20opportunities%2C%20many%20end%20up%20accepting%20these%20low-ball%20offers%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20is%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20addressing%20this%20pay%20gap%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20the%20ones%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20present%2C%20we%20are%20engaged%20with%20more%20than%20150%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women%20in%20their%20workforce.%20Our%20team%20speaks%20to%20these%20companies%2C%20discusses%20their%20salary%20bands%2C%20and%20tells%20them%20what%20the%20industry%20standard%20is%20and%20what%20they%20should%20ideally%20offer.%20If%20the%20companies%20express%20a%20willingness%20to%20interview%20our%20applicants%20and%20discuss%20salary%20offers%20commensurate%20with%20the%20experience%20and%20skill%20set%20of%20our%20applicants%2C%20we%20make%20the%20effort%20to%20help%20them%20diversify%20their%20workforce.%20If%20the%20companies%20are%20hesitant%2C%20we%20step%20back%20and%20ask%20our%20applicants%20not%20to%20compromise%20on%20their%20salary%20demand%20and%20not%20go%20for%20their%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20person%20they%20recommend%20to%20companies%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20these%20job%20interviews.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20we%20are%20running%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20applicant%20is%20capable%20enough.%20As%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20we%20connect%20these%20applicants%20to%20mentors%20who%20help%20them%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20and%20fill%20up%20the%20necessary%20gaps%20in%20their%20skill%20sets.%20Moreover%2C%20these%20mentors%20also%20interview%20our%20applicants%20for%20certain%20roles.%20So%2C%20we%20only%20deliver%20these%20interviewed%20people%20to%20the%20companies.%20So%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20person%20(applicant)%20is%20capable%20and%20that%20the%20%5Bjob%5D%20profiles%20are%20filtered%20at%20our%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SheWork%20is%20a%20Pune-based%20company%20dedicated%20to%20hiring%20women%20in%20tech%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368867%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20Companies%20need%20to%20address%20unconscious%20bias%20against%20hiring%20women%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2Ffizkes)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20pay%20gap%2C%20Pooja%20also%20argues%20that%20at%20the%20recruiter%20level%2C%20there%20is%20still%20an%20unconscious%20bias%20against%20hiring%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20see%20is%20that%20if%20companies%20receive%20five%20CVs%20(three%20women%20and%20two%20men)%2C%20they%20will%20interview%20the%20two%20men%20and%20give%20them%20priority.%20If%20these%20men%20are%20rejected%2C%20only%20then%20will%20they%20give%20the%20female%20job-seeker%20a%20chance.%20That%20unconscious%20bias%20still%20exists%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20Despite%20all%20the%20noise%20around%20hiring%20more%20women%2C%20recruiters%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20still%20lack%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20so.%20This%20unconscious%20bias%20has%20to%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20can%20take%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20address%20these%20biases%20by%20providing%20some%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F164442%2Fmaddie-award-mg-changemakers-gender-equity-india-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20sensitivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20training%20to%20their%20recruiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20at%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20what%20we%20do%20is%20mask%20the%20CVs%20sent%20to%20companies.%20All%20we%20give%20them%20is%20their%20first%20names%20and%20skill%20sets.%20We%20do%20not%20put%20up%20their%20marital%20status%2C%20surnames%2C%20genders%20(although%20that%E2%80%99s%20sometimes%20difficult%20with%20first%20names)%2C%20etc.%20When%20we%20send%20their%20CVs%2C%20we%20highlight%20their%20skill%20sets%2C%20the%20projects%20they%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20on%2C%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%2C%20roles%2C%20responsibilities%2C%20etc.%20Once%20they%20are%20selected%20for%20interviews%2C%20we%20communicate%20to%20the%20panels%20at%20these%20companies%20overseeing%20hiring%20to%20record%20them.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20record%20the%20interviews%20so%20that%20our%20candidates%20aren%E2%80%99t%20asked%20questions%20that%20go%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20professional%20capabilities.%20Recording%20these%20interviews%20makes%20recruiters%20conscious%20of%20the%20questions%20they%20ask%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20has%20also%20changed.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%20%3C%2Fem%3Eapplicants%20are%20only%20looking%20for%20remote%20opportunities%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20telling%20companies%20to%20only%20give%20our%20applicants%20remote%20opportunities.%20The%20current%20trend%20is%20moving%20towards%20hybridisation.%20So%2C%20we%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20our%20applicants%20hybrid%20work%20opportunities%20but%20with%20some%20flexibility%20as%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20an%20applicant%20just%20had%20a%20baby%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20has%20come%20back%20from%20maternity%20leave%2C%20we%20negotiate%20with%20the%20company%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20companies%20have%20a%20five-day%20policy%20of%20coming%20to%20the%20office%2C%20we%20help%20our%20applicant%20negotiate%20for%20three%20days%20because%20she%20has%20a%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThankfully%2C%20we%20have%20some%20industry%20leaders%20supporting%20our%20work.%20They%20are%20lending%20us%20a%20helping%20hand%20in%20making%20their%20workplace%20more%20flexible.%20On%20our%20end%2C%20we%20encourage%20our%20applicants%20that%20if%20they%20want%20equal%20pay%20and%20opportunity%2C%20they%20also%20need%20to%20work%20a%20little%20harder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20part%2C%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20come%20up%20with%20their%20%3Cem%3EGyno-Care%20Program%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20free%20health%20check%20up%20camps%20for%20women%20IT%20professionals%20in%20association%20with%20partner%20companies%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20SheWork%20(%40shework.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENeed%20more%20help%20from%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20her%20experience%2C%20Pooja%20believes%20that%20the%20greatest%20resistance%20%5Bto%20women%20working%20regularly%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%5D%20usually%20comes%20from%20families%20more%20than%20companies%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20women%20really%20need%20is%20more%20help%20from%20their%20families%20like%20their%20husbands%2C%20in-laws%2C%20and%20relatives%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20household%20work.%20They%20must%20contribute%20a%20little%20more%20to%20unburden%20women%20from%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20household%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20availability%20of%20daycare%20facilities%20in%20cities%2C%20there%20are%20families%20who%20do%20not%20like%20their%20children%20to%20be%20put%20up%20there.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20personal%20choice%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20put%20your%20child%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%20or%20not%20but%20as%20times%20change%2C%20so%20should%20families.%20If%20families%20can%20support%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20their%20children%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%2C%20it%20would%20help%20working%20women%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20must%20do%20more%20to%20accommodate%20women%20by%20investing%20and%20setting%20up%20creches%20and%20day-care%20facilities%20for%20children%2C%20she%20argues.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Sydney%2C%20I%20remember%20visiting%20a%20company%20that%20had%20a%20feeding%20room%20for%20new%20mothers%20and%20a%20creche%20facility%20overseen%20by%20a%20qualified%20caretaker%2C%20where%20children%20could%20play.%20Companies%20in%20India%20can%20afford%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20facilities%20and%20must%20progress%20with%20the%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SheWork.in%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fdiverse-office-portrait-talented-indian-girl-2078917600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728099000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D368833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pooja%20Bangad%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SheWork%2C%20overcame%20family%20expectations%20to%20change%20women%E2%80%99s%20roles%20in%20tech.%20SheWork%20helps%20women%20return%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%20after%20breaks%2C%20fights%20for%20equal%20opportunities%2C%20and%20challenges%20the%20gender%20bias%20that%20holds%20women%20back%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20grow%20and%20succeed%20in%20their%20careers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Speaking%20up%20After%2025%20Years%3A%20How%20Education%20Helped%20This%20Survivor%20Break%20the%20Cycle%20of%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20violence%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20five-year-old%20once%20visited%20a%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Didi%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(elder%20sister).%20The%20older%20woman%20called%20the%20young%20girl%20into%20a%20room%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20undress%2C%20and%20she%20complied.%20What%20happened%20next%20would%20give%20the%20young%20girl%20sleepless%20nights%20for%20many%20years%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20child%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Allahabad%20in%20Uttar%20Prad