%20documentary%20%E2%80%98Son%20Rise%E2%80%99%20(2019)%20%E2%80%94%20which%20follows%20the%20journey%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366915%2Fsunil-jaglan-selfie-with-daughter-bibipur-village-haryana-daughters-day-women-empowerment-female-foeticide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emen%20breaking%20the%20shackles%20of%20patriarchy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20that%20it%20takes%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20pluck%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%2C%20Bakshi%20was%20stunned%20when%20the%20boy%20continued%20in%20earnest%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20have%20the%20same%20courage%20to%20have%20these%20conversations%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20know%20they%20might%20not%20always%20have%20a%20positive%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20she%20ever%20fathom%20Son%20Rise%20would%20create%20whistleblowers%20of%20patriarchy%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20going%20by%20her%20observations%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20screening%20across%2071%20countries%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20global%20%23HeForShe%20movement%2C%20the%20boy%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20wanting%20to%20fight%20gender%20bias.%20The%20sentiment%20is%20mirrored%20by%20police%20officers%2C%20CEOs%20of%20multinational%20corporations%2C%20the%20elite%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20in%20rural%20hinterlands%2C%20she%20has%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlways%20one%20to%20target%20the%20status%20quo%20through%20layered%20rhetorics%2C%20Bakshi%20says%20Son%20Rise%20was%20a%20step%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%20The%20narrative%20isn%E2%80%99t%20preachy%3B%20there%20is%20no%20moral%20policing.%20Instead%2C%20the%20cinematic%20masterpiece%20makes%20the%20most%20of%20its%2050%20minutes%20to%20leave%20the%20audience%20with%20some%20food%20for%20thought.%20The%20film%20uncovers%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276654%2Funique-wedding-tradition-rituals-breaking-norms-patriarchy-atheist-couple%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egendered%20realities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Haryana%20by%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20changemakers%20instead%20of%20the%20perpetrators.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20sets%20it%20apart.%20It%20beckons%20you%20to%20look%20towards%20the%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-500x707.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Son%20Rise%20(2019)%20is%20a%20documentary%20film%20by%20award-winning%20filmmaker%20Vibha%20Bakshi%20that%20highlights%20the%20men%20challenging%20patriarchy%20in%20Haryana%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-500x707.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-768x1086.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-1086x1536.jpg%201086w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-1448x2048.jpg%201448w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-1200x1697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960-150x212.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSonRise_poster_page-0001_11zon-1727704960.jpg%201585w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESon%20Rise%20(2019)%20is%20a%20documentary%20film%20by%20award-winning%20filmmaker%20Vibha%20Bakshi%20that%20highlights%20the%20men%20challenging%20patriarchy%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20every%20screening%20ends%20with%20thunderous%20applause%20and%20Bakshi%E2%80%99s%20shelves%20are%20laden%20with%20awards%20%E2%80%94%20including%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20cinema%20honour%2C%20the%20National%20Film%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Film%E2%80%99%20(non-feature)%20and%20%E2%80%98Best%20Editing%E2%80%99%20(non-feature)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Global%20SABRE%20Award%20(2022)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20validation%20Bakshi%20values%20most%20comes%20when%20men%20approach%20her%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20happening%20is%20not%20right.%20What%20can%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20film%20of%20hers%20is%20a%20wish%2C%20a%20hope%2C%20a%20prayer%20for%20a%20world%20where%20men%20become%20allies%20and%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Gender%20inequality%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20hinterlands%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3Edhoti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wraparound%20cloth%20worn%20around%20the%20legs)%20and%20chequered%20scarf%20protect%20the%20men%20of%20Haryana%2C%20as%20they%20sit%20in%20clans%2C%20sipping%20hot%20cups%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20camera%20pans%20to%20the%20oldest%20among%20the%20group%2C%20possibly%20in%20his%20sixties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20girls%20be%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reaffirms%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20for%20female%20foeticides.%20Another%20from%20the%20group%20chips%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20ultrasounds%20to%20peek%20into%20the%20womb.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20successful%20in%20these%20killings%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20look%20to%20the%20men%20on%20screen%20for%20answers.%20Statistics%20point%20us%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20skewed%20sex%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201901%2C%20the%20state%20had%20867%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%20its%20total%20population%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Statistical%20Handbook%20of%20Haryana%202020-21.%20Over%20100%20years%20later%2C%20as%20per%20Census%202011%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20remained%20equally%20worrying%20at%20879%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%20These%20are%20proof%20of%20the%20antiquated%20practice%20of%20sex%20determination%20in%20Haryana%2C%20that%20continues%20far%20from%20the%20glare%20of%20modern%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Filmmaker%20Vibha%20Bakshi%20focuses%20on%20gender%20parity%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20sensitising%20mindsets%20through%20her%20films%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C