3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%E2%80%99m%20from%20Raigad%20district%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20South%20Goa.%20Visiting%20the%20beach%20nearby%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it%20and%20learnt%20how%20to%20swim%20in%20the%20sea%20with%20my%20friends.%20But%20I%20also%20saw%20many%20people%20drowning%20in%20the%20sea%20and%20that%20left%20a%20real%20impression%20on%20me.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20wanted%20a%20job%20where%20I%20could%20save%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Drishti%20Marine%20was%20operational%20in%202008%2C%20Shashikant%20was%20a%20lifeguard%20working%20for%20another%20company%20contracted%20by%20the%20tourism%20department%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267418%2Fgoa-government-school-robotics-coding-scheme-first-india-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoa%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20there%20was%20little%20to%20no%20coordination%20in%20rescue%20efforts.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20the%20people%20in%20charge%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20I%20had%20swam%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20to%20rescue%20someone.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20proper%20equipment%20like%20a%20surfboard%2C%20walkie-talkie%2C%20lifeguard%20jeep%2C%20or%20jet-ski%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20coordination%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20professionalism%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20lack%20of%20beach%20safety%20and%20the%20number%20of%20drowning%20deaths%20Goa%20saw.%20Matters%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202007%20when%20the%20state%20unfortunately%20saw%20200%20people%20drown%20off%20the%20coastline%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20Somani%2C%20founder%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Drishti%20Marine%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20events%20of%202007%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20prompted%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%20and%20put%20together%20an%20efficient%20system%20to%20safeguard%20lives%20along%20beaches.%20One%20of%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20to%20appoint%20a%20professional%20agency%20for%20enhancing%20beach%20safety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drishti%20'Lifesavers'%20(lifeguards)%20saving%20lives%20in%20Goa.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-270x300.jpg%20270w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-768x855.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-150x167.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDrishti%20%E2%80%98Lifesavers%E2%80%99%20(lifeguards)%20saving%20lives%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20was%20tasked%20by%20the%20Goa%20Government%20to%20curb%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171819%2Fdelhi-police-hero-rescue-drowning-child-inspirational%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrowning%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20beaches.%20Once%20it%20was%20awarded%20a%20contract%20to%20offer%20lifeguard%20services%20for%20the%20state%2C%20Shashikant%20was%20among%20the%20first%20lifeguards%20to%20join%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20Drishti%20in%20July%202008%2C%20they%20put%20me%20through%20a%2045-day%20training%20course%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20lifeguarding%20and%20how%20to%20use%20the%20new%20equipment%20given%20to%20us.%20There%20was%20a%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20safety%20here.%20In%20my%20previous%20job%2C%20we%20would%20get%20no%20backup%20during%20rescue%20efforts.%20Now%2C%20whenever%20we%20go%20out%20on%20a%20rescue%2C%20we%20are%20supported%20by%20jet%20skis%2C%20backup%20lifeguards%2C%20etc.%20Also%2C%20we%20receive%20continuous%20training%20and%20have%20reorientation%20sessions%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20methods%20and%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBraving%20the%20waves%3A%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Drishti%20Marine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Drishti%20becoming%20the%20designated%20agency%20to%20provide%20lifeguard%20services%20also%20prompted%20Ashwin%20Ghag%2C%20a%20former%20national-level%20swimmer%2C%20to%20leave%20Pune%20for%20Goa%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%201999%20to%202008%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20swimming%20coach%20for%20children%20in%20Pune%2C%20after%20which%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20senior%20lifeguard.%20Before%20my%20swimming%20coach%20and%20lifeguard%20career%2C%20I%20was%20a%20national-level%20swimmer.%20I%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20father%20to%20become%20a%20lifeguard.%20Watching%20him%20work%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159192%2Fpune-drowning-lives-raju%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_