%20passengers%20board%20steamers%2C%20and%20remnants%20of%20the%20colonial%20era%2C%20the%20South%20Bombay%20pincode%20is%20almost%20a%20bubble%20frozen%20in%20time.%20Copious%20amounts%20of%20ice%20were%20manufactured%20every%20day%2C%20which%20made%20their%20way%20from%20the%20factory%20to%20the%20restaurants%2C%20fish%20markets%20and%20vegetable%20markets%20across%20South%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20beguiling%20history%20of%20the%20ice%20factory%20that%20drew%20Malik%20to%20this%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20also%20the%20intention%20to%20convert%20this%20place%20into%20a%20meeting%20spot%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative-minded%20folk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20isn%E2%80%99t%20such%20a%20place%20in%20the%20city%20where%20architects%20and%20designers%20can%20meet%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20projects%20that%20are%20touted%20as%20sustainable%20these%20days%20subvert%20this%20claim.%20But%20Malik%20was%20keen%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20ice%20factory%20stayed%20true%20to%20its%20intentions.%20The%20reasons%20for%20this%20lie%20in%20his%20childhood%20fascinations%2C%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Shimla%2C%20I%20was%20extremely%20drawn%20to%20nature.%20Those%20experiences%20have%20been%20my%20guide%20in%20this%20journey%20of%20architecture%20and%20design.%20There%20can%20be%20nothing%20more%20sustainable%20than%20nature%20itself%2C%20and%20through%20my%20work%2C%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20look%20at%20a%20more%20meaningful%20approach%20to%20sustainability.%20This%20means%20understanding%20the%20region%20we%20are%20building%20in%2C%20the%20climate%20of%20the%20region%2C%20the%20flora%20and%20fauna%2C%20the%20local%20building%20materials%2C%20an