men%20during%20their%20most%20difficult%20postpartum%20periods.%20%E2%80%9CA%20woman%20going%20through%20a%20cocktail%20of%20emotions%20is%20blamed%20for%20not%20producing%20enough%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20month%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20Gayathri%E2%80%99s%20anxiousness%20turned%20into%20guilt.%20She%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20friends%20and%20cousins%2C%20but%20they%20advised%20her%20to%20consider%20formula%20feeding.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20determined%20to%20breastfeed%20my%20child%20as%20breastfed%20babies%20have%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20developing%20many%20diseases%20like%20asthma%2C%20obesity%2C%20ear%20infections%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Gayathri%20launched%20her%20startup%20NariCare%20to%20revolutionise%20breastfeeding%20support%20to%20new%20mothers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20Gayathri%20launched%20her%20startup%20NariCare%20to%20revolutionise%20breastfeeding%20support%20for%20new%20mothers.%3C%2Ffigca